-- TeleSign’s Mobile Services Unit Starts Operation in Serbia
-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 2013-03-22T12:49:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-22/telesign-s-mobile-services-unit-starts-operation-in-serbia.html
TeleSign Mobile, a unit of U.S.
Internet security and authentication company TeleSign Corp.,
opened an operations center in Belgrade with plans to employ 100
workers.  The London-registered Telesign Mobile sees “Serbia as a
key growth area,” according to the statement e-mailed by the
U.S. embassy in Belgrade, quoting Steve Jillings, TeleSign’s
chief executive officer. It didn’t specify the value of the
investment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
 msavic2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  